  31 Jan 2013; Chris Reffett <creffett@gentoo.org> -glosung-2.1.3.ebuild,
  -glosung-3.2.2.ebuild, -glosung-3.4.2.ebuild, -glosung-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  30 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> glosung-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #315419

  29 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> glosung-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #315419

*glosung-3.6.2-r1 (29 Jan 2013)

  29 Jan 2013; Chris Reffett <creffett@gentoo.org>
  +files/glosung-3.6.2-scons-respectflags.patch, +glosung-3.6.2-r1.ebuild,
  -glosung-3.6.2.ebuild:
  Revision bump, add patch to allow SCons to use environment CC, CFLAGS, and
  LDFLAGS, remove auto-set CFLAGS such as -g.

*glosung-3.6.2 (21 Jan 2013)

  21 Jan 2013; Chris Reffett <creffett@gentoo.org>
  +files/glosung-3.6.2-glib-includes.patch, +files/glosung.desktop,
  +glosung-3.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add patch to fix build with modern glib, ship a .desktop file
  due to non-UTF-8 validation errors in the built in .desktop file. Fix
  dependencies.

  04 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> glosung-2.1.3.ebuild,
  glosung-3.2.2.ebuild, glosung-3.4.2.ebuild, glosung-3.5.2.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

  27 Mar 2011; Nirbheek Chauhan <nirbheek@gentoo.org> glosung-2.1.3.ebuild,
  glosung-3.2.2.ebuild, glosung-3.4.2.ebuild, glosung-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Fix slot-dep on gtk+

